#compdef cyrus-mbtest
# Documentation: (no upstream tool by this name)
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-16
# Verified: no `mbtest` binary exists in cyrus-imapd. Repository search of
# cyrusimap/cyrus-imapd confirms only `imap/mbtool.c` (the binary
# `mbtool`); no `imap/mbtest.c`. cyrusimap.org has no mbtest(8) manpage.
# The completion appears to have been generated from a non-existent
# binary. Kept as a conservative stub per "do not delete files" directive;
# users who want completion for the real tool should use cyrus-mbtool
# (separate file).
# Removed from prior file: fabricated -h/--help/-V/--version flags and
# bogus man.archlinux.org search URL.

# cyrus-mbtest: NOT A REAL CYRUS BINARY (see cyrus-mbtool instead)
local curcontext="$curcontext" ret=1
_arguments -C \
  '*:arg:_files' && ret=0
return ret
